---
title: Sweet Chilli-Ginger Pork & Slaw Bowl with Crispy Shallots & Spring Onion
description: Sweet chilli and ginger is a pairing that we didn’t see coming but are happy to have in our hearts (and mouth)! It’s the contrast
that we’ve fallen in love with and how it goes perfectly with beef strips as a glaze.

